latestPosts.caption:
Guys, I can’t even express how excited I was when I heard that Honey Singh was coming to Adelaide, Australia. I decided on the spot that I would go, even if I had to go alone. I still remember telling my cousin when he visited from India that whenever I came to India, he had to take me to a Honey Singh concert. Who would have thought that he would come to Adelaide and I’d get the chance to see him live? I am incredibly thankful for this opportunity. I used to pray for this moment, and even though I might have forgotten about it over time, today my dream has come true. Trust me guys, dreams can come true in unexpected ways. Apart from that, it was an amazing night.😍🫶🏻
